tps://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-says-no-second-album-any-time-soon-3806132">写作书籍和汽车一起被盗</a>，迫使她告诉歌迷，她期待已久的第二张专辑“很快”不会发行。</p><p>与此同时，史密斯将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james">詹姆斯</a>一起参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/james-announce-huge-summer-2025-uk-tour-with-razorlight-happy-mondays-shed-seven-across-various-shows-3810849">2025 年英国巡演</a>的选定日期，包括在林肯、普利茅斯和科尔切斯特的演出 - 请访问 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/james-tickets/artist/741201" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>查找门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-a-smith-has-gear-including-gifted-guitars-and-essential-medication-stolen-in-london-3824223">汤姆·A·史密斯 (Tom A. Smith) 的装备包括天才吉他和在伦敦被盗的“基本药物”</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
